article_id:2375,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627624800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The newly added 5★ adventurer Summer Leonidas (shadow) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Gala Audric (light/axe)</div><div>5★ Summer Leonidas (shadow/lance)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627624800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1628056799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
